result::Result::<&T, E>::copied.doc:
Maps a `Result<&T, E>` to a `Result<T, E>` by copying the contents of the
`Ok` part.

# Examples

```
let val = 12;
let x: Result<&i32, i32> = Ok(&val);
assert_eq!(x, Ok(&12));
let copied = x.copied();
assert_eq!(copied, Ok(12));
```

